	<h1 class="title">佛学院应该是什么样子？不是你想的那么有仪式感</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-15 10:02:10 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/12099/medium/12099.jpg?1436878461" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="12099" data-title="《佛学院应该是什么样子？不是你想的那么有仪式感》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12099/medium/12099.jpg?1436878461" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12099.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
